text: Renée C. Harris is an American singer, dancer and actress. Her career was launched as an 18-year-old with the role of Dorothy Gale in the touring version of The Wiz.Jet Dec 2 1976Ebony Jr. April 1977 p.8 ==Discography== *"Doctor Music" released with B-side "Yesterday Girl" in Germany 1977 *"I Close My Eyes And Count To Ten", B-side "It's Morning" 1978 ==References== Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
